&lt;!-- end snippet --&gt;

There&#39;s a detailed explanation given on [w3Schools](https://www.w3schools.com/jsref/jsref_tofixed.asp) with this link having the [example to it](https://www.w3schools.com/jsref/tryit.asp?filename=tryjsref_tofixed).

